[SN]TITLE[SN]
Limavady: 'Substantial sum of money' stolen from cash machine

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A substantial sum of money has been stolen from a cash machine in County Londonderry.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The contents of an ATM on Main Street in Limavady were stolen at around 05:00 BST this morning, police said.
Thieves broke into a charity shop to get access to the machine.
Police are appealing for anyone with information about the incidents to contact them on the non-emergency number 101.
